2	// for the FitCommerce platform.
3	//
4	// This package will contain the following job implementations (Prompts 4 and 7):
5	//
6	//   - Auto-close job: periodically scans for orders in "created" status that have
7	//     exceeded the 30-minute auto-close timeout and transitions them to "auto_closed".
8	//
9	//   - Cutoff evaluation job: checks active group-buy campaigns at their cutoff time,
10	//     evaluating whether the minimum quantity threshold has been met, and transitions
11	//     campaigns to "succeeded" or "failed" accordingly.
12	//
13	//   - Backup job: orchestrates database backup creation, compression, SHA-256 checksum
14	//     computation, encryption of the archive, and recording of the backup run metadata.
15	//
16	//   - Retention cleanup job: identifies entities that have exceeded their retention
17	//     policy period and performs soft-delete or archival as appropriate, respecting
18	//     the 7-year financial and 2-year access log retention requirements.
19	//
20	//   - Variance deadline job: scans open variance records that are past their
21	//     resolution due date and triggers escalation notifications for overdue items.
22	//
23	// All jobs are designed to be run as goroutines with configurable intervals and
24	// graceful shutdown support via context cancellation.
25	package jobs
26	
